highlights.text: “Sugar On My Tongue” by Tyler, The Creator is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Thailand, up 18 spots at #62.
“One Of My Life” by BLVCKHEART and K6Y has been on Viral Songs Thailand the longest, at 262 days straight.
YUNGTARR has the most spots on Viral Songs Thailand. “โคมไฟระย้า” is the highest at #34.
